cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper introduces a novel formulation of active learning as a reinforcement learning problem, which suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The focus on cross-lingual named entity recognition also suggests that it could belong to the sub-category of machine translation (cs.CL).
